Prerequisites
=================

  1.   Ruby-1.8.1 or better
       http://www.ruby-lang.org/en/

  2.   Iterator-0.8 or better
       http://rubyforge.org/frs/?group_id=18&release_id=512


Installation
=================

Follow these 3 steps in order to install.
last step may require 'root' permissions.

       ruby install.rb config
       ruby install.rb setup
       ruby install.rb install

Now go to the 'samples/' directory and have fun.


Any Trouble ?
=================

If you experience problems with installation, then please 
goto this homepage and submit a bug-report. 
http://rubyforge.org/tracker/?atid=149&group_id=18&func=browse

or mail to me directly
Simon Strandgaard <neoneye@gmail.com>
